  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"f77bc246-da65-4b88-8441-7df6378076b5\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661421/Subdivision+Surfaces\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661421\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Subdivision Surfaces</a> for more information on subdivision surfaces.</p></div></div><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"6598b129-9b5e-478d-9523-eaba6c4a466d\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Poorly tessellated (non-subdivision) surfaces may show artifacts when rendering like dark edges and outlines. It's recommended to render smooth subdivisions to avoid this artifact. You may also use polygons with no normals defined and then subdivide, RenderMan will compute the normals for you.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><p>To render a polygon as a subdivision surface, add the RenderMan tab to the OBJ node. Toggle the &quot;Render Polygons As Subdivision&quot; parameter found in the Geometry &gt; SubdivisionMesh rollout. You will also need to set the Style parameter to Catmull-Clark, Bilinear, or Loop. </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"subdiv.PNG\" width=\"456\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644237/subdiv.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125706&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=427&amp;height=456\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644237/subdiv.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125706&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"342\" data-width=\"320\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644256\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"subdiv.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644237\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c5e6925f-e8a3-473b-90bb-62e5e76e4cb6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644237/subdiv.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125706&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=427&amp;height=456 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644237/subdiv.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125706&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=427&amp;height=456 1x\"></span><p><br/></p><p>To match geometry from Maya (a common request and our default) you will see:</p><ul><li><p>Catmull-Clark</p></li><li><p>Interpolation: Sharp Creases and Corners</p></li><li><p>Facevarying Boundary: New Style, internal only</p></li></ul><p>Details on these settings along with illustrations can be found on the RenderMan page for <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661421/Subdivision+Surfaces\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661421\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Subdivision Surfaces</a></p><p /><p>This image was rendered using the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661805/PxrVisualizer\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661805\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrVisualizer</a> integrator in Houdini.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"rfhSubD_ExampleOn.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644237/rfhSubD_ExampleOn.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644237/rfhSubD_ExampleOn.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644253\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfhSubD_ExampleOn.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644237\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ef6e6826-967c-463f-8eb6-cec1dc08e277\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644237/rfhSubD_ExampleOn.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644237/rfhSubD_ExampleOn.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433125705&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p><br/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/> </p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
    }
